Package GIS

Class Game

  • java.lang.Object
    • GIS.Game
  • public class Game
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a Game. A game is an object with five ArrayList associated with it. one ArrayList for fruits, one for pacmans, one for ghosts, one for boxes , one for players, one for corners. This class will receive a list of board data. it will read the list and add each element to the correct list.
    Author:
    Shay Naor , Alex VAisman
